                        <amp-lightbox id="product-pop-return" layout="nodisplay" animate-in="fly-in-top" scrollable>
                            <div class="lightbox">
                                <div class="lightbox-content">
                                    <p>We want you to feel comfortable and confident when shopping at STUNRING Jewelry,
                                        that’s why we offer a 30-day return & exchange policy. If for any reason you're
                                        not satisfied with your purchase, you may return or exchange the unused item in
                                        its original condition as long as you contact us within 30 days from the
                                        delivered date.</p>
                                    <p><strong>Please note: Items can be exchanged no more than once. The time frame for
                                            this must not exceed 30 days from when the original order was
                                            received.</strong></p>
                                    <p>If for any reason you're not satisfied with your purchase, please email
                                        service@stunring.com and we'll provide you with further instructions on where
                                        returns should be shipped, and the amount you will be refunded. Refund amounts
                                        for returned items will be credited to you in the same currency and using the
                                        same exchange rate as your original tender. Returns must be made within 30 days
                                        of delivery. Customers will be charged for shipping costs (this includes returns
                                        and resends).</p>
                                    <h2 class="font-semibold text-lg my-1">Return &amp; Exchange Conditions</h2>
                                    <ol>
                                        <li>Items returned without authorization will not be accepted.</li>
                                        <li>The time frame for return & exchange must not exceed 30 days from when the
                                            original order was received.</li>
                                        <li>All items must be returned in their original condition with tag, without
                                            scratches or signs of wear, and must not be resized or altered in any way.
                                        </li>
                                        <li>When returning or exchanging items, customers must use a shipping method
                                            that has tracking on it. Returns or exchanges with no tracking ID will not
                                            be processed.</li>
                                        <li>For return, any promotional gifts received must be included with the
                                            returned items. Otherwise, the retail price of the promotional gift will be
                                            deducted from the refund.</li>
                                    </ol>
                                    <p><span style="color: #ff0000;">Note: Please do not send your return to the
                                            address on your package. That is not our return address and will affect the
                                            processing of your return.</span></p>

                                    <h2 class="font-semibold text-lg my-1">Non-Refundable & Non-Exchangeable Items</h2>
                                    <ol>
                                        <li>Personalized items with “engravings” and “photos”, such as rings, necklaces
                                            and bracelets, are non-refundable or exchangeable..</li>
                                        <li>Special order items such as those with custom sizes and colors are not
                                            refundable and exchangeable. (Custom sizes are those that charge extra $15)
                                        </li>
                                        <li>Items without jewelry tag or that have been worn, damaged or altered are not
                                            refundable or exchangeable, and will be returned to the customer at their
                                            expense.</li>
                                        <li>Items that were worn, or sent to you as Replacement/Exchange are not
                                            refundable or exchangeable.</li>
                                    </ol>

                                    <h2 class="font-semibold text-lg my-1">Refunds</h2>
                                    <p>Returns will be processed within 5 days upon receipt of your package. The refund
                                        will be issued to your original payment account and cannot be returned to
                                        alternate cards or different forms of payment.</p>
                                    <p><strong>Note: The standard shipping rate before discount will apply and is
                                            non-refundable. Although you may have enjoyed free or undervalued shipping,
                                            we do incur the original cost of shipping for every order. Therefore, we do
                                            not refund our original shipping cost.</strong></p>
                                    <h2>STUNRING will reimburse customer $10 as the return shipping fee under the
                                        following circumstances.</h2>
                                    <ol>
                                        <li>Customer received the wrong item.</li>
                                        <li>The item is broken, defective, or has an incorrect engraving. (For broken or
                                            defective items, customers must contact STUNRING within 48 hours of
                                            receiving their order.)</li>
                                    </ol>

                                    <h2 class="font-semibold text-lg my-1">Cancellation</h2>
                                    <p>We stand behind our jewelry to satisfy you with every order and want your order
                                        to be made just the way you want it! Please review your
                                        personalization/engraving/special order information before submitting your
                                        order. Check spelling, dates and names carefully. You are welcome to contact us
                                        if you have questions before placing your order.</p>
                                    <p>Generally, all personalized/engraved/special order items will be sent into
                                        production in 8 hours after we receive the payment. Therefore, any cancellations
                                        after that time will incur a corresponding material and processing fee.</p>
                                    <p>Please refer to below details:</p>
                                    <ol>
                                        <li>If the cancellation is made less than 8 hours after the order was placed,
                                            there would be no cancellation fee.</li>
                                        <li>If the cancellation is made between 8 to 24 hours after the order was
                                            placed, there would be a 10% cancellation fee.</li>
                                        <li>If the cancellation is made 24 hours after the order was placed, there would
                                            be a 30% cancellation fee.</li>
                                    </ol>
                                    <p>For general orders, items will be sent into production in 8 hours after we
                                        receive the payment. Therefore, any cancellations after that time will incur a
                                        corresponding material and processing fee.</p>
                                    <p>Please refer to the below details:</p>
                                    <ol>
                                        <li>If the cancellation is made less than 24 hours after the order was placed,
                                            there would be no cancellation fee.</li>
                                        <li>If the cancellation is made over more than 24 hours after the order was
                                            placed, there would be a 10% cancellation fee.</li>
